  "title": "3mths Senior Executive Assistant, HR Shared Services - No exp needed, $2.5K to $3K #HKH",
  "description": "<ul><li>Ensure related documentations are P-filed accordingly.</li><li>Assist in updating, maintaining, and approving of HR data for existing staff in myHR</li><li>Assist in verifying and updating onboarding data for New Hires & offboarding data for Resignees via myHR</li><li>Deliver the HR activities that meet the service level agreement (SLA) and key performance indicator (KPI) </li><li>Ensure record in myHR are maintained accurately based on agreed procedures and team standards</li><li>Adhoc duties as per assigned</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum Diploma in ANY field</li><li>Min 1 year of HR experience </li></ul><p>Interested candidates, please email your resume to <em><strong>kevynhuang@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></em><br /></p><p><em>Huang Jingsheng Kevyn</em></p><p><em>Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Lifescience)</em></p><p><em>Company EA Licence number : 99C4599</em></p><p><em>Personnel EA License: R1333338</em></p>",
